{"tid":165430,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"新一代 SE 推出先兆？美國零售商 iPhone SE 減價發售！","createTime":"2017-03-21T10:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T04:49:59.000Z","uid":6587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0e57ccb45b2940f56368a0c9e7f9a329f5f816","tid":165430,"uid":6587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"除了特別的推廣活動或是節日之外，iPhone 甚少會突然減價發售，但如果 iPhone 突然減價促銷的話，可能意味著一些事情。前有消息指出，蘋果的發佈會將會在未來一個月舉行，雖然這次的發佈會重點，是在於全新 iPad 的面世。不過 iPhone SE 亦是眾人的焦點之一。早前有消息指出，蘋果有可能會提早為 iPhone SE 更新，以減少對新旗艦 iPhone 的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前美國著名零售商 BestBuy 突然為 iPhone SE 推出減價優惠，分別把兩款 iPhone SE 的售價都下調多達 100 美元，16GB 版本只需 300 美元，而 64GB 版本亦只需 350 美元。這台 iPhone SE 採用了 iPhone 5s 的機身設計，但用上了強大的效能規格，吸引了不少對舊 iPhone 設計喜愛的人士轉用。同時日前大陸的淘貓天貓亦推出了 iPhone SE 的減價優惠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n豉油：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/03/21/iphone-se-sale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F03%2F21%2Fiphone-se-sale%2F&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm99U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6b1898ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/03/21/iphone-se-sale/</a>"},{"pid":"5719fbdd3d2045bc6f93c0727d8135eef3b432b6","tid":165430,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"出左成年既機減價又拎黎吹水 se肯定唔會有新一代 有早就流出可靠消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70738e406fb3c61251e02c4f867fc9d1ffe22513","tid":165430,"uid":45840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左成年既機減價又拎黎吹水 se肯定唔會有新一代 有早就流出可靠消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"c446550f9be9fce74d8528b3831969411d8396d5","tid":165430,"uid":72751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"但好期待出新一代se<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6cd2b8eb